The paper focuses on scene text detection using deep learning techniques, which is a common topic in computer vision (cs.CV). The paper also discusses the use of weakly supervised and semi-supervised learning, which are subfields of machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also mentions the use of high-level annotations for character searching, which is related to information retrieval (cs.IR) and natural language processing (cs.CL).
